	<Usage>held in 1 hand</Usage>
	<Description>Performers popularized these bundles of aromatic herbs to calm the mind and ward off misfortune before a big show, though soldier bards have found them especially useful for clearing fear during particularly tumultuous battles. Adding this catalyst to a &lt;i&gt;soothe&lt;/i&gt; spell also causes the spell to reduce the target's frightened condition value by 1.</Description>
